LanguageData.RobCoQuestOfferText:
A recently breached RobCo management vault has spilled one of the wasteland's most dangerous secrets back onto the market. A cache of platinum chips was recovered from the vault and sold through the Mojave Express to multiple buyers.
Each lead points to a different courier and a different faction sponsor. If you move quickly, you may be able to seize one of the chips before it disappears into another power bloc.
{0}
